Python --> Application
Python --> Inbuilt packages will be available
    1. math,os,sys,logging,etc.
Python --> 3rd party packages
    1. Tensorflow, PyTorch, Pandas, DataPrep, "virtualenv"

We can install our python 3rd party modules using python installation package manager --> pip

1. pip install virtualenv

Python Virtual Environment:
1. activate
2. deactivate

--> by default pyenv will in deactivate state
--> We have to activate it.
    1. we have to run one bash program

    relative path==> <Parentdirectory>/lms/bin/activate
                 ==> <Parentdirectory>/lms/Scripts/activate

    2. source <relative path>

--> Deactivating
    1. deactivate